item.title: Number of questions on skills/pking/stalls/teleports/etc
item.dc:creator: @nerdboyxx nerdboyxx
item.description:
@nerdboyxx wrote:

funny, it didnt show up before. I might have looked when I was further down the code thank you anyway I will check now…

…checked, yeah I think I searched thieving instead of stall (noob spotlight on me) thanks heaps. I changed so now its a bit fairer (you could get a red phat from a stall wtf lol) so you get a fairer sum of money. Now people actually have to work for it lol

I have a follow-up question; how do I edit teleport spells? Example, I want to change where everyone starts off to a place like edgeville or Lumbridge. All I need to do is change the teleport spells to send the player to a set coordinate, but I have no idea how. Probably something easy like search teleport but if anyone could tell me how to exactly access it that would be really good to

thanks again.
